name: Jerry Clubb
text: This restaurant is my preferred one. I visit a lot of restaurants but to this restaurant I go the most. The crew is very friendly and the food they cook is so good. I never miss an opportunity to have a nice dinner here. I highly recommend this place.

name: Darrick Cooper
text: I always stop purchasing some food in this spot. I enjoyed the prompt customer service and well prepared dishes. I recommend this place.
